    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Request someone’s authorization to be able to send critical messages from",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "this app. The framework shows an authorization alert for each recipient,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "one at a time, up to the maximum of recipients the framework allows, which you",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "can determine by examining the constant ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.messages/documentation/Messages/MSCriticalSMSMessenger/maximumCriticalMessagingRecipients",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can call this method multiple times with the same",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "or different recipients, the framework displays the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "permission alert with the latest block of recipients. When you call",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "this method subsequent times, all previous recipients move",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "automatically to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.messages/documentation/Messages/MSCriticalMessagingError/notAuthorized",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " status.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Upon success, the method returns a dictionary that maps recipients to their",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "corresponding authorization status.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
